Doskocil Cos talk sey de don extend deir bank account till May 31 1990 to give am more time to sell Wilson Food Corp, dey sell deir fresh meat market.

Di company go repay $58 million on top Dec. 31 and $15 million on March 31.

Di company get di debt wen e pay $155 million to buy Wilson last year.

An agreement wey dem dey call George Gillett to sell di Wilson asset for $150 million naira, when di buyer, one company wey be sey dey controlled by George Gillett no fit secure mortgage.

